en_28544_0	Brigadier Harendra Ranasingha of the Special Forces Regiment assumed office on Thursday (12) as the 36th Director, Directorate of Operations at the Army Headquarters during a brief ceremony.
en_28544_1	After brief religious observances, the newly-appointed Director Operations left his signature in an official document, signifying the acceptance of his new office.
en_28544_2	Staff officers in the Directorate and other ranks attended the inauguration of the office.
en_28544_3	He succeeded Brigadier Upali Rajapaksha who has been appointed as the Deputy General Officer Commanding, 53 Division.
